== Trivia ==
Considering that Lt. Worf's R'uustai is an AoE (or Area of Effect) attack, this skill can be used to allow more powerful characters to launch powerful attacks, making Lt. Worf a very dangerous Tier 1 character that can decimate teams with ease if not taken out early in the fight.[[Category:Yellow]]
